/* ============================================================
   new-templates-o.js — fifteenth batch of generated templates.

   Same shape as new-templates.js (see that file for the task tuple
   format). Batch O is about plans whose shape is set by a constraint
   most template libraries quietly drop: a standard that requires
   consultation as scheduled activity, a programme that reaches a
   defensible state instead of finishing, a schedule owned mostly by
   somebody outside your company, and a reveal where every surface has
   to switch in the same moment.

   Task tuple: [name, startOffsetDays, durationDays, percentComplete,
                hexColor, { phase|indent|who|after|milestone }]
   ============================================================ */

